{"tid":398643,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[fat fat]商戶料iPhone X炒貴1倍　8及8 Plus貴幾百","createTime":"2017-09-13T10:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T10:52:14.000Z","uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"388e32fbeaf270a1b5f558f061f530714d90c314","tid":398643,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"美國蘋果公司推出一系列新產品，其中iPhone 8和iPhone 8 Plus於周五(15日)接受預訂！手機商戶姚先生表示，睇淡iPhone 8及iPhone 8 Plus炒價，預計只會比原價貴幾百港元，因今次焦點都落在iPhone X，相對較少人選擇這2款機，今天(13日)起已開始接受預訂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他預料iPhone X價格可以炒上一倍，因iPhone X在外型及功能上都有較大改動，且是十周年特別版，出貨又少，令炒風更熾熱，他已預留數百萬至1千萬港元收機。</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n姚又表示，舊款iPhone在宣布推出新機前，已經降價約1千至2千港元不等，他估計已差不多跌至見底，不會再跌太多。 <br />\n<br />\n上車不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/mobile/bkn-20170913124748047-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170913%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170913124748047-0913_00822_001.html&d=lPUdG0AmzE4D6hJl1L6OR5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b0e68c07\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170913/mobile/bkn-20170913124748047-0913_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"38b04dee8cb43c5bf4f761f61919fe0b754fc719","tid":398643,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"Stronghold"},{"pid":"7227360e31358e7543e9ef1eb04bf65d937d169a","tid":398643,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}